+	could hide characters, if _window.padding.x_ allows characters behind the
+	scrollbar.
+
+	Default: _0.5_
+
+*fade_time_in_secs* <float>
+
+	Time (in seconds) the scrollbar takes to disappear in _"Fading"_-_mode_.
